[30;1m130 | [0m[35msend a message.[0m
[30;1m131 | [0m[35mIf your ASGI server of choice adheres to the spec version ``2.4``, this receive[0m
[30;1m132 | [0m[35mqueue can be safely disabled for a slight performance boost by setting[0m

[30;1m71 | [0m[35m    The router treats URI paths as a tree of URI segments and searches by[0m
[30;1m72 | [0m[35m    checking the URI one segment at a time. Instead of interpreting the route[0m
[30;1m73 | [0m[35m    tree for each look-up, it generates inlined, bespoke Python code to[0m

[30;1m75 | [0m[35m    processing quite fast.[0m

[30;1m4 | [0m[35m====================[0m
[30;1m5 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m6 | [0m[35mGenerating a CSV (or PDF, etc.) report and making it available as a downloadable[0m
[30;1m7 | [0m[35mfile is a fairly common back-end service task.[0m
[30;1m8 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m9 | [0m[35mThe easiest approach is to simply write CSV rows to an ``io.StringIO`` stream,[0m
[30;1m10 | [0m[35mand then assign its value to :attr:`resp.text <falcon.Response.text>`:[0m

[31m--[ [0m[34mMatch #[0m[33m1062[0m[34m of [0m[33m1388[0m[31m ]--[0m
   Rule Id: [34mBD000600[0m
       Tag: [34mSecurity.Backdoor.LOLBAS.Windows[0m
  Severity: [36mModerate[0m, Confidence: [36mLow[0m
  Filename: [33m/falcon-4.0.2/docs/api/multipart.rst[0m
   Pattern: [32m\s(advpack\.dll|appvlp|at|atbroker|bash|bginfo|bitsadmin|cdb|certutil|cl_invocation\.ps1|cl_mutexverifiers\.ps1|cmd|cmdkey|cmstp|comsvcs\.dll|control|csc|cscript|csi|devtoolslauncher|dfsvc|diskshadow|dnscmd|dnx|dotnet|dxcap|esentutl|eventvwr|excel|expand|extexport|extrac32|findstr|forfiles|ftp|gfxdownloadwrapper|gpscript|hh|ie4uinit|ieadvpack\.dll|ieaframe\.dll|ic|infdefaultinstall|installutil|jsc|makecab|manage-bde\.wsf|mavinject|mftrace|microsoft\.workflow\.compiler|mmc|msbuild|msconfig|msdeploy|msdt|mshta|mshtml\.dll|msc|msxsl|netsh|odbcconf|pcalua|pcwrun|pcwutl\.dll|pester\.bat|powerpnt|presentationhost|pubprn\.vbs|rcsi|reg|regasm|regedit|register-cimprovider|regsvcs|regsvr32|rpcping|rundll32|runonce|runscripthelper|sc|schtasks|scriptrunner|setupapi\.dll|shdocvw\.dll|shell32\.dll|slmgr\.vbs|sqldumper|sqlps|sqltoolsps|squirrel|syncappvpublishingserver|syncappvpublishingserver\.vbs|syssetup\.dll|te|tracker|tttracer|update|url\.dll|verclsid|vsjitdebugger|wab|winrm\.vbs|winword|wmic|wscript|wsl|wsreset|xwizard|zipfldr\.dll)\s[0m
[30;1m61 | [0m[35m                    form_data[part.name] = await part.text[0m
[30;1m62 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m63 | [0m[35m.. note::[0m
[30;1m64 | [0m[35m   Rather than being read in and buffered all at once, the request stream is[0m
[30;1m65 | [0m[35m   only consumed on-demand, while iterating over the body parts in the form.[0m
[30;1m66 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m67 | [0m[35m   For each part, you can choose whether to read the whole part into memory,[0m

[30;1m1009 | [0m[35m----------------------------------------------------------------------------[0m
[30;1m1010 | [0m[35mFalcon skips processing the response body when, according to the HTTP[0m
[30;1m1011 | [0m[35mspec, no body should be returned. If the client[0m
[30;1m1012 | [0m[35msends a HEAD request, the framework will always return an empty body.[0m
[30;1m1013 | [0m[35mFalcon will also return an empty body whenever the response status is any[0m
[30;1m1014 | [0m[35mof the following::[0m
[30;1m1015 | [0m[35m[0m
